title: [PS3] Warhammer  40,000 : Space Marine
description:
Unleash destruction in the first third person action shooter set in the Warhammer 40,000 universe.

* Step fearlessly into the heart of combat as an unstoppable Space Marine.
* Use an innovative new combat system to switch seamlessly from high calibre long-range weapons to devastating close-combat strikes.
* Jump into a rich universe of awe-inspiring landscapes, deadly enemies, immense battles and ruthless annihilation.
* Form your own Space Marine squad or Chaos Space Marine war band via PlayStation Network and face off in 8 versus 8 online matches.
